IPCONFIG(1)

NAME
    ipconfig - show or renew IPv4 configuration

SYNOPSIS
    ipconfig
    ipconfig /all
    ipconfig /renew
    ipconfig /release

DESCRIPTION
    ipconfig is a compatibility-style frontend for the SmallOS IPv4
    configuration commands.

COMMANDS
    /all
        Show full network configuration.

    /renew
    renew
        Request IPv4 configuration via DHCP.

    /release
    release
        Clear IPv4 configuration.

SEE ALSO
    ip(1), dhcp(1), netinfo(1)
